- full-service restaurants, with full menu and waiting service;
- limited-service restaurants or quick service restaurants (QSR), with full menu but pay-as-you-order such as fast food or turo-turo type*;
- cafes/bars/pop-ups (selected menu with few chairs and tables);
- kiosks and stalls (purely retail, to be consumed elsewhere); and
- catering or 100% home delivery.

Full-service restaurants, limited-service restaurants and cafes/bars/pop-ups may also offer "to go" or "take away" services.
